2014-11-10  libmoepgf v1.1   Stephan M. Guenther  <moepi@moepi.net>

* Changed license for the library from GPL version 2 to LGPL version 2.1 to
allow easier integration. Note that the license of the benchmark application
remains GPL version 2.

* Added runtime-detection of NEON SIMD.

* Added custom PRNG moepgf_rand().

* Changed build-system to autotools.

